Pick up the blue candle holder on the shelf in the wall.
Turn around to face the living room table.
place the blue candle holder on the living room table.

place the red candle holder on the living room table.

Pick up the blue container from the cupboard.
Turn around and face the small round black table.
Put the blue container down on the table in front of the remote.

Pick up the red vase from the shelf.
Walk back over to the small round black table.
Put the red vase down on the table to the right of the blue container.

Pick up the blue vase off of the black shelf.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right to face the coffee table.
Put the blue vase on the coffee table.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right to face the white shelving unit.
Pick up the red vase off of the white shelving unit.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then turn right to face the coffee table.
Put the red vase on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Move two vases to the coffee table.
